                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d224">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Swenson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Copenhagen</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-02-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 15, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Swenson reports that the Danish Government is in favor of Department’s
                    proposal and will accept the same as soon as the acceptance of France, England,
                    and Germany is announced.)</p>
            </div>
